OL,3,CBin workers to launch all-out
OL,4,Cindefinite strikes in Birmingham
OL,6,FBin strikes in Birmingham are set to
OL,7,Fescalate to indefinite all-out action,
OL,8,Fas workers vote to decide whether to
OL,9,Fcontinue through spring and summer.
OL,11,FMore than 350 workers began strike
OL,12,Faction in January over the scrapping
OL,13,Fof the waste collection and recycling
OL,14,Fofficer role - which resulted in pay
OL,15,Fcuts of up to #8,000 for 150 people.
OL,17,FWalk-outs had been scheduled for 26
OL,18,Fand 27 February, and 3, 4, 6 and 10
OL,19,FMarch.
