OL,6,FBirmingham City Council said: "This
OL,7,Fescalation of industrial action will
OL,8,Fmean greater disruption to residents -
OL,9,Fdespite the fair and reasonable offer
OL,10,Fthat the council made to Unite the
OL,11,FUnion.
OL,13,F"To the small number of workers whose
OL,14,Fwages are impacted ongoing by the
OL,15,Fchanges to the service (of whom there
OL,16,Fare now only 40) we have already
OL,17,Foffered alternatives, including highly
OL,18,Fvaluable LGV Driver Training for
OL,19,Fcareer progression and pay, and other
OL,20,Froles in the council equivalent to
OL,21,Ftheir former roles.
